snippet.title: Crash Team Racing: Retro Fueled - Mod Launch Trailer - Download Link
snippet.description:
Enjoy the original CTR from 1999 with Blue Fire, U-Turning and every turbo pad being USF!

Download file: http://beyondtwinsanity.com/mods/

This mod is only compatible with the NTSC-U version of the game. Simply open the Crate Mod Loader, download the Retro Fueled pack, select it with the loader and have fun!

Thumbnail credit goes for artist @Rezknil: https://www.instagram.com/rezknil/

If you want to contribute with the CTR modding community, please consider joining our discord server: https://discord.gg/56xm9Aj
